Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.crypto.modes.kgcm

Class KGCMUtil_256

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.crypto.modes.kgcm.KGCMUtil_256
public class KGCMUtil_256 extends Object
Utilities for the GF(2^m) field with corresponding extension polynomial: GF (2^256) -> x^256 + x^10 + x^5 + x^2 + 1 The representation is little-endian arrays of 64-bit words
